PROGRAM 12 : Convert the following english statment into a c program"ask the user for their name and age , then print : hello<name>you are <age>years old"

#include<stdio.h>
int main()
{
char name [50];
int age ;
printf (" enter your name : ");
scanf("%s",name );
printf ("enter your age : ");
scanf("%d",&age );
printf("Hello % s, you are % d years old .\n",name ,age);

}


OUTPUT 

enter your name : Pavi
enter your age : 17
Hello Pavi, you are  17 years old .

[Process completed - press Enter]
